stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Planning

    Planning --> InProgress : Start Work
    Planning --> Archived : Cancelled/Rejected

    InProgress --> OnHold : Pause Work
    InProgress --> Completed : Work Finished
    InProgress --> Archived : Abandoned

    OnHold --> InProgress : Resume Work
    OnHold --> Archived : Abandoned while on hold

    Completed --> Archived : File Away

    Archived --> [*] : End of Lifecycle